// HistoryDiffSettingsDropdown
// Settings dropdown for the history diff banner in the editor toolbar.
// Allows changing view mode (inline/side-by-side) and compare mode
// (vs-current / vs-previous).

FUNCTION HistoryDiffSettingsDropdown(settings, onSettingsChange, hasPreviousVersion, onClose) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Renders two radio-button sections: View Mode and Compare.
  vs-previous option is disabled when hasPreviousVersion is false.
  Closes on click outside or Escape.

---

FUNCTION handleViewModeChange(viewMode) -> void
  Calls onSettingsChange({viewMode, compareMode: settings.compareMode}).

---

FUNCTION handleCompareModeChange(compareMode) -> void
  Calls onSettingsChange({viewMode: settings.viewMode, compareMode}).
